<div class="whl-page">

  <!-- ── HERO ── -->
  <div class="whl-hero">
    <div class="wave-field" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="wave wave--back"></span>
      <span class="wave wave--mid"></span>
      <span class="wave wave--front"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="whl-hero-inner">
      <div class="whl-eyebrow">Wholesale · Now Onboarding Retailers</div>
      <h1 class="whl-title">Put Happie on your shelf.</h1>
      <p class="whl-sub">Caffeine-free, all-natural sparkling drinks made with functional mushrooms — the non-alcoholic option shoppers are actually looking for. Retail-ready 6-packs and master cases, third-party tested every batch.</p>
      <a href="#order" class="btn-primary btn-lg">Start a Wholesale Order →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── WHY STOCK US ── -->
  <div class="whl-section">
    <div class="whl-inner">
      <div class="whl-section-head">
        <div class="whl-section-eyebrow">Why Retailers Stock Happie</div>
        <h2 class="whl-section-title">A can that earns its shelf space</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="whl-grid">
        <div class="whl-card">
          <span class="whl-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 3h18v4H3zM5 7v13h14V7M9 11h6"/></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Retail-ready</h3>
          <p>Shelf-stable, retail-priced 6-packs and 24-can master cases. Loose and case formats available for however your set is built.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="whl-card">
          <span class="whl-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M8 12l3 3 5-6"/></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>The category shoppers want</h3>
          <p>Non-alcoholic, caffeine-free, and functional — sitting right where better-for-you soda, sparkling water and alcohol alternatives are growing fastest.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="whl-card">
          <span class="whl-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3l7 4v5c0 4-3 7-7 9-4-2-7-5-7-9V7z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Tested every batch</h3>
          <p>Third-party lab tested at an ISO/IEC 17025-accredited lab. Certificates of Analysis available for every batch you carry.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="whl-card">
          <span class="whl-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 7h16M6 7V5h12v2M8 7v13h8V7"/><path d="M10 11h4"/></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Bold on the shelf</h3>
          <p>Three high-contrast flavors — Blue Razzberry, Mango Mimosa, Watermelon — with can art built to catch an eye from across the aisle.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── ORDERING WIDGET (Airgoods) ── -->
  <div class="whl-section whl-order-section" id="order">
    <div class="whl-inner whl-inner--narrow">
      <div class="whl-section-head">
        <div class="whl-section-eyebrow">Wholesale Ordering</div>
        <h2 class="whl-section-title">Browse & order below</h2>
        <p class="whl-order-note">New account? Registering takes a minute. Approved buyers see wholesale pricing, minimums and lead times right in the catalog.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="whl-widget">
        {%- comment -%}
          The Airgoods wholesale catalog renders here.

          PREFERRED: paste the Airgoods embed into this Page's body content in
          Shopify admin (Online Store → Pages → Wholesale → Content, in HTML/<>
          mode). It prints below via {{ page.content }}.

          IF Shopify strips the Airgoods <script> from the page body, paste the
          embed markup directly between the two markers below instead and it will
          load from the theme.
        {%- endcomment -%}

        {%- if page.content != blank -%}
          {{ page.content }}
        {%- else -%}
          {%- comment -%} ===== AIRGOODS EMBED — paste widget code here ===== {%- endcomment -%}
          {%- comment -%} ===== /AIRGOODS EMBED ===== {%- endcomment -%}

          <div class="whl-widget-placeholder">
            <strong>Wholesale catalog loads here.</strong>
            <span>The Airgoods ordering widget hasn't been added yet. Until then, reach us directly to place a wholesale order.</span>
            <a href="mailto:{{ shop.email }}?subject=Wholesale%20order%20—%20Happie%20Fusion" class="btn-ghost">Email us to order →</a>
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>

      <p class="whl-contact">Questions before you order? <a href="mailto:{{ shop.email }}?subject=Wholesale%20inquiry%20—%20Happie%20Fusion">{{ shop.email }}</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<style>
